-- Alstom to hold board meeting on Friday afternoon - source 
-- By Gilles Guillaume
-- Fri Apr 25, 2014 04:13AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, April 25 (Reuters) - French engineering group Alstom <ALSO.PA> will hold a board meeting on Friday afternoon, a source close to the matter told Reuters.

The source did not say what Alstom's board would discuss at the meeting. Alstom declined to comment. News of the meeting comes as shares in Alstom were suspended on Friday at the request of the French regulator.